<li>"The Word According to Tom Wolfe": <a href="http://tv.nationalreview.com/uncommonknowledge/post/?q=ZWY2NTViMTM4NGU3YjM2NTAwNTA4ZTQ0NGRjMzcxOTQ=" class="external text" title="http://tv.nationalreview.com/uncommonknowledge/post/?q=ZWY2NTViMTM4NGU3YjM2NTAwNTA4ZTQ0NGRjMzcxOTQ=" rel="nofollow">Episode 1</a>, <a href="http://tv.nationalreview.com/uncommonknowledge/post/?q=MjA0ZjhiMWI1YTQxNGY0YmM0Y2YwMTc4NDIyYmQwMDU=" class="external text" title="http://tv.nationalreview.com/uncommonknowledge/post/?q=MjA0ZjhiMWI1YTQxNGY0YmM0Y2YwMTc4NDIyYmQwMDU=" rel="nofollow">Episode 2</a>, <a href="http://tv.nationalreview.com/uncommonknowledge/post/?q=N2RhZWYzZGE1ZGE2NmYzOTQxNDFiZGZmZTc1NTE0YTI=" class="external text" title="http://tv.nationalreview.com/uncommonknowledge/post/?q=N2RhZWYzZGE1ZGE2NmYzOTQxNDFiZGZmZTc1NTE0YTI=" rel="nofollow">Episode 3</a>, <a href="http://tv.nationalreview.com/uncommonknowledge/post/?q=MDg4NDI2M2RhOTQ4MzgyZmE4ZTY2OGU3NTc3ZjJmNzM=" class="external text" title="http://tv.nationalreview.com/uncommonknowledge/post/?q=MDg4NDI2M2RhOTQ4MzgyZmE4ZTY2OGU3NTc3ZjJmNzM=" rel="nofollow">Episode 4</a>, and <a href="http://tv.nationalreview.com/uncommonknowledge/post/?q=MjRmYTYzYWI0YjQzYmFlYjkyODIwYTFmZDg3ZGRmNGU=" class="external text" title="http://tv.nationalreview.com/uncommonknowledge/post/?q=MjRmYTYzYWI0YjQzYmFlYjkyODIwYTFmZDg3ZGRmNGU=" rel="nofollow">Episode 5</a> from <a href="/wiki/National_Review" title="National Review">National Review</a></li>
